<doc id="538459" wikidata="Q3110985" url="?curid=538459" title="Sedna Planitia">
<text>Sedna Planitia is a large lowland area of Venus, south of Ishtar Terra. 
It is thought to be lava-covered and similar to a lunar mare. Its name is derived from the Inuit sea goddess.

